{"tid":27012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"10後吹水區","createTime":"2016-12-07T05:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T18:27:58.000Z","uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43ed1f581764232cee7dedd3adab233704c1f002","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"戴緊媽咪買俾我既新錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31956e0c1bc86a093abef554f49f07446b06c8d4","tid":27012,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"你地出毛未？"},{"pid":"b809ac276adb72c65228c6ecf29e3a2e2847232f","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地出毛未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有好多頭毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8951c84785857cac7764c54b48f93349c8a66925","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"連登無10後？"},{"pid":"c221ba0bf054a525c1ff4d0dd7650bd331eecc64","tid":27012,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死撚開啦<br />\n生齊毛味呀"},{"pid":"fd9f1e988ab20b9bee88272a58c0befc8209d0b6","tid":27012,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母死撚開啦<br />\n生齊毛味呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗱，師兄10後可以係1910後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48be4238bda875d91f056c13f0ae0c3e545c764a","tid":27012,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"幫助別人改變命運，自己的命運也就同時得到潛移默化的改變。<br />\n<br />\n經常看到一些人戒色文章學習了不少，覺悟也看似提高了，但心魔來臨時就又成了擺設，極度痛苦地懊悔著。原因就在於覺悟還不夠全面、清晰和精煉。對此，我力荐的方法就是鼓勵吧友，解答疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n萬丈深淵中懊喪的你請不要再抱怨自己什麼都做到了卻還屢戒屢破，破戒，一定是有原因的，破戒，一定說明你還有做得不夠好的地方。<br />\n平庸者往往一面在對眼前機會的嫌棄中游手好閒，一面覺得自己是&quot;世界上最努力的人&quot;，而對這個&quot;不公平的世界&quot;產生消極、仇恨。而不凡之人時刻保持著一顆謙謹的心，永不停息地檢視並改進自己。<br />\n<br />\n屢戒屢破，嗯？那請每天毫不敷衍地解答10個、20個甚至更多吧友的疑惑、真心地鼓勵他們，看看自己還會不會瘋狂破戒。"},{"pid":"d879c03c7e3a36237efc472574eaec81126029b0","tid":27012,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死𡃁妹"},{"pid":"ddac4bb7e45fb598bf5bd67125f2b6132f0bf54d","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母死撚開啦<br />\n生齊毛味呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗱，師兄10後可以係1910後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄你好醒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008f7b73727c703f27a39db6110ce02e8421afcf","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死𡃁妹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呀婆黎架on9"},{"pid":"11a84d8f2d748c19a4f37cb8193cadd2177d8e36","tid":27012,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7442848239e47af0d9725021b47fbd71b1a158a","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOk"},{"pid":"1b3629cc90b7feda1382018f6bd8d3734f1c9fb2","tid":27012,"uid":52086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n130+歲 驅風清熱"},{"pid":"d32e2db843871e84f4abe59971df267ac02504e5","tid":27012,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n130+歲 驅風清熱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces